ack_quote: "Much love, dude. You guys rule. Good luck. Play hard, dude. For real, you guys are all with me."

"Thanks, guys. Good luck to all of you."
"Stay strong, stick to the plan, finish them off."
"That was a great compliment. Thank you."
"You guys are strong. Kick some ... butt."
"You blindsided! Nice! That's how you vote somebody off!"
"Still smiling, guys. Have fun. Love ya."
"I'd like my hat back at some point. 'Night guys."
"Some advice, next time y'all lose a challenge, a\nlittle less cursing off your tribe might help.... It's been a pleasure."
"Oh, I'm gonna be good and drunk in the next five minutes."
"Hey, good luck with that food situation."

"It's been one hell of a time, guys. Vinaka."

"You guys have no idea how much fun I had with all you. It was truly a pleasure."
"Did you know? Why are you smiling. Oh my God I can't handle you right now."
"Good luck, you guys. I love you all. I really do."
"Good luck to you all. Well played."
"I will say this. The person who orchestrated this, you now have my vote for a million dollars. It's up to someone else to make a bigger move."
"Good luck. I'll see you all soon."
"The lord gives. The lord takes away. What a fun experience. Hopefully I'll see you soon."
"It's been such a pleasure, guys. I know it's a game but, really, take care of yourselves and each other. Good luck."

"Y'all made the right decision. Love you."

"Dang, Elaine, I knew it. All right. I'll see you all later. Wednesday night at 8."
"Bye guys, good luck. Love you Tommy."
"Good luck, guys. Did not see it coming."
"I'll do my best to join you again tomorrow."
"It was a pleasure. Tony: I love you. Crush it tomorrow, alright?"
Good luck, guys. Gonna eat so much food."
"See you guys in the real world."
"Proud of you, Frannie, for winning today."
"Hey, one of y'all win it for me. I love you all. Good luck."
"Thank you, everybody. It's been a pleasure."
"My vote's going to the best player."
"Love you guys. Good luck! Give 'em hell."
